### GoalKeeper Dash — API reference / contract collection
### Works with the VS Code "REST Client" extension (or JetBrains .http runner).
### Full run flow: auth -> session -> submit -> leaderboards.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@api = {{baseUrl}}/api/v1

### --- Public ---

# List active nations
GET {{api}}/nations

###

# Global national board (public, defaults to active season)
GET {{api}}/leaderboards/nations?limit=10

###

# Global personal board (public)
GET {{api}}/leaderboards/users?limit=10

### --- Auth ---

# Dev login (only when app.oidc.dev-login-enabled=true; NEVER in prod).
# For real providers use POST {{api}}/auth/google|facebook|apple with a verified IdP idToken.
# @name login
POST {{api}}/auth/dev
Content-Type: application/json

{ "idToken": "demo-player-1" }

###

@accessToken = {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
@refreshToken = {{login.response.body.refreshToken}}

# Refresh access token (rotates the refresh token)
POST {{api}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{ "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}" }

###

# Logout (revoke refresh token)
POST {{api}}/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{ "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}" }

### --- Profile & nation ---

# Current profile, nation, lock status, active season
GET {{api}}/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

# Update display name (rate-limited)
PATCH {{api}}/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "displayName": "TheWall" }

###

# Pick / switch nation (409 NATION_LOCKED after first validated score)
PUT {{api}}/me/nation
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "nationCode": "MAR" }

### --- Game session + submit ---

# Open a server-issued, single-use session
# @name session
POST {{api}}/sessions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "mode": "TOURNAMENT" }

###

@sessionId = {{session.response.body.sessionId}}
@nonce = {{session.response.body.nonce}}

# Submit a score (consumes the session)
POST {{api}}/sessions/{{sessionId}}/submit
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nonce": "{{nonce}}",
  "score": 880,
  "mode": "TOURNAMENT",
  "durationMs": 142300,
  "eventSummary": {
    "shotsFaced": 120, "saves": 88, "goalsConceded": 9,
    "maxCombo": 14, "perfectSaves": 5, "schemaVersion": 1
  }
}

### --- Leaderboards ---

# Headline dual board (personal-within-nation + nation-in-world)
GET {{api}}/leaderboards/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

# Within-nation board
GET {{api}}/leaderboards/nations/MAR/users?limit=20

###

# A closed season's final board (pass seasonId)
GET {{api}}/leaderboards/nations?seasonId=REPLACE_WITH_SEASON_ID&limit=20
